title: Potato-Topped Cannellini Bean Curry Pie with Roasted Cauliflower & Mustard Seeds
description: This easy to make veggie deluxe pie is a taste sensation. Roasted cauliflower, seasoned cannellini beans and veggies
hidden under a blanket of mashed potatoes is already a great dinner, but bake it into a pie and serve with brown
mustard seeds and dinner just become a lot more exciting!

